{
  "texts": [
    "DataCore services were utilized to prepare the data as described below.",
    "Acompliant private instance of ChatGPT (Microsoft Azure OpenAI Service) was utilized for this study.",
    "LlaMA-2 (\"Llama-2-70b-chat\" version) was evaluated on two A100 Nvidia GPUs on our local high performance computing servers.",
    "This Diagnostic/Prognostic study designed to validate the diagnostic accuracy of two LLMs (ChatGPT and LlaMA-2) in extracting cognitive exam dates and scores, follows the TRIPOD Prediction Model Validation reporting guidelines (S1 Checklist) [61].",
    "An original cohort of 135,307 clinical notes corresponding to inpatient, outpatient, and emergency department visits between January 12th 2010 and May 24th 2023, which included any of the following keywords ('MMSE', 'CDR,' or 'MoCA' case-insensitive) were identified (see Fig 1)."
  ]
}